<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 32px; font-size: 16px !important;">6月22日，江西软件职业技术大学组织开展2024届毕业生党员座谈会暨党纪学习教育专题党课活动。学校党委书记、督导专员江延湖出席活动并为毕业生党员讲授“最后一堂党课”。学校党委委员、党委组织部部长程杨胜主持。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-align: center;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-26%2009%3A34%3A24656c17b93aabd35618729a25df9b3f8.jpg?Expires=2034725664&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=hXigMTENIQntXGE9uJK%2F%2B7Z5YAk%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-26%2009%3A34%3A24656c17b93aabd35618729a25df9b3f8.jpg?Expires=2034725664&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=hXigMTENIQntXGE9uJK%2F%2B7Z5YAk%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></a></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">江延湖以《以严明的纪律，推动全面从严治党纵深发展》为题，从深刻认识纪律严明的重大意义、准确把握《条例》新修订的内容、作为青年党员如何学习贯彻好《条例》三个方面，重点解读了《中国共产党纪律处分条例》修订的主要内容、重大意义、鲜明特点等，并按照修订前后对照表，结合违纪典型案例，带领大家学习。他勉励大家，在未来的职业发展道路上，要牢记“共产党员”的第一身份，持续锤炼党性修养，坚定拥护“两个确立”，坚决做到“两个维护”；要扣好廉洁从业的“第一粒扣子”，严守《条例》的“六项纪律”，树立正确的权力观、事业观、政绩观；要牢记习近平总书记嘱托，把人生理想融入党和国家事业，把知识转化为推动工作的动力源泉，创造出无愧于党的教育、无愧于母校的培养、无愧于青春年华的光荣业绩。</span></p><p><br/></p>